<h2 local-id=3D"d619b851-866c-40ce-885a-cb469ac3fb72" id=3D"CourseDetailsSc=
reen-8.3CourseDetailsScreen">8.3 Course Details Screen</h2>
<p local-id=3D"0acefacc-a281-46f6-8558-fa7be4842b0c"><strong>Overview:</str=
ong><br>
The Course Details screen provides a comprehensive view of all course infor=
mation, status progression, and management capabilities. It serves as the c=
entral hub for viewing and managing individual courses throughout their lif=
ecycle.</p>
<p local-id=3D"655ed694-b703-4288-836d-7dc9c77b8957"><strong>Access Points:=
</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"1485ad3f-ea28-45d4-b6f2-3bd3ac0726cd">
<li local-id=3D"47e2430a-3334-45cc-8595-1016b6c78915">
<p local-id=3D"9123ff2e-1f6d-4f5e-b6a1-c652b29c760f">Click on course code h=
yperlink in Course List</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b1dbb724-1b31-42cc-8ad3-ae4f15562b22">
<p local-id=3D"67508668-01a9-419f-bd7b-b5b0fb77d429">Navigate from Master C=
alendar or PIC Calendar</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a6025cc3-7a03-41d4-90ec-9cb0cffcbda5">
<p local-id=3D"0478d378-048e-4b4e-9a64-09ed63040971">Direct URL: <code>/cou=
rses/[courseId]</code></p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"3e72bbd9-ee7e-4c23-8654-ddc497f257e3"><strong>Authorization:=
</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"89060eea-e950-48bd-9c2c-5197aa7d2f23">
<li local-id=3D"a43de72f-d327-44eb-96cc-3eff50a7e5dd">
<p local-id=3D"6b33cbe6-0f36-4953-a6c8-da434e419052">All users can view cou=
rses based on their role and region/channel permissions</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a80dd077-7978-424a-a143-7cd8fdb2146f">
<p local-id=3D"9209c854-1ce4-42cd-a845-ad61375cbfc9">Edit/Delete/Cancel act=
ions follow role-based authorization matrix (see Section 8.5)</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"9906473e-cc31-4dd2-9cff-6aba2081ffb3"><strong>Page Structure=
:</strong><br>
The Course Details page consists of:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"d6b38be6-4a8c-4a2f-a0e5-d9fdf5e7ae28">
<li local-id=3D"69d9cade-58da-41dc-805e-abd32bac8386">
<p local-id=3D"39cd6a39-b340-4535-8b85-4ee8d54d5910">Header section with co=
urse title and action buttons</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c15a0226-5fd0-4a58-858e-cf1c863bca70">
<p local-id=3D"848671ea-1d9e-4274-a881-fa2aba9a3abe">Tab navigation (Genera=
l, Planning, Participants, Checklist, History)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"97d22412-8b20-4221-a94e-b40a10dfd42b">
<p local-id=3D"60e28903-0a69-4660-b095-4045e371f301">Content area displayin=
g tab-specific information</p></li>
</ol>
<hr local-id=3D"834eb222-f550-478f-9b50-debcdbfce3a8">
<h3 local-id=3D"d3a91684-701e-4810-9bb1-070e5c4ecd12" id=3D"CourseDetailsSc=
reen-8.3.1.2CourseStatusTimeline">8.3.1.2 Course Status Timeline</h3>
<p local-id=3D"a07661de-1807-41d0-9e68-90837a793be4"><strong>User Story:</s=
trong> <br>
AS a user viewing course details <br>
I NEED a visual timeline showing the course status progression <br>
SO THAT I can quickly understand the course lifecycle, track status changes=
, and see who performed each action and when</p>
<p local-id=3D"89a35ac6-4379-4f77-8969-a88b23afe1a0"><strong>Acceptance Cri=
teria:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"fad18daf-292e-4498-89c9-f4b7b9e313c5">
<li local-id=3D"1a07ac59-0572-48a8-b7d2-55d5d07a2c36">
<p local-id=3D"4c376d53-f2ea-427e-a5ce-0d87e453e6b6"><strong>Timeline Displ=
ay:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"422cef73-6e38-4952-bb68-c89dd9e5583a">
<li local-id=3D"8f3a4018-e79c-46d9-9f91-0e89b7797ad3">
<p local-id=3D"7e484e81-852c-412a-b3d9-894df734f75f">Status timeline displa=
yed at the top of Course General Tab</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2531f243-488b-4cab-b076-00a08fef928b">
<p local-id=3D"952414b1-5f65-4ffa-bbb0-598cb99957e9">Shows all status miles=
tones in chronological order</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"54e228fd-1e90-4bfb-91d8-12118fc9d3f9">
<p local-id=3D"4e17587d-2687-4e17-9ac9-aa95e83bac53">Visual indicators for =
completed, current, and pending statuses</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fb48efd6-6d48-45de-bbc3-644ef9ad89f8">
<p local-id=3D"5c0208a6-b461-4072-8c1e-fca1978fe10b">Click to expand/collap=
se detailed information for each milestone</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"d89120dc-9c51-4119-bca5-805f0023dfed">
<p local-id=3D"d68be551-d551-498e-a93c-aa494183beeb"><strong>Status Milesto=
nes Displayed:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"81090b0d-8eb2-43e8-827e-7495fc76b338">
<li local-id=3D"d543a3b8-0f02-4780-ace8-c5850c892605">
<p local-id=3D"98afb0f2-082d-4602-879a-1f37d735e606">NEW - Course Created</=
p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f80c8756-dfb1-483c-a803-eb5471930bbf">
<p local-id=3D"a5cb9c87-00b0-402c-acb4-67321b7cb6eb">REGISTERED - Trainer R=
egistered</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"47c678e5-e933-4a99-9eb4-e9b30d78e61a">
<p local-id=3D"5c919748-67fe-4a36-a737-a9c163766fd1">APPROVED - Course Appr=
oved</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cda1e6c4-4250-4a01-ad68-719d40140249">
<p local-id=3D"72bf5b08-fd39-498d-b077-33d565de55ba">WAITING_APPROVAL_EDIT =
- Edit Pending (shown only when applicable)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e5f74959-c496-4ef7-bba8-674f0e4bf6f6">
<p local-id=3D"ba15baf6-4c2c-4e9d-94cc-70d9ee8495c9">IN_PROGRESS - Course S=
tarted (Auto)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6085d78b-8313-41ce-8afd-a111f474d272">
<p local-id=3D"eb1c07e3-b6e3-4fa1-b320-e1c4acb68af8">FINISHED - Course Comp=
leted</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"124022a3-324a-4409-bc0b-7a5162e6d4e1">
<p local-id=3D"d8bd4cef-375e-425b-82f6-ff07294e55ec">CANCEL - Course Cancel=
led (shown if course was cancelled)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4df5dbf5-e1ed-4736-a455-bcb476433847">
<p local-id=3D"280cb9a1-55c1-40bf-a78e-b9b117c7b6f2">WAITING_APPROVAL_CANCE=
L - Cancel Pending (shown only when applicable)</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"9d3e199a-ddf3-4f26-9af4-f981d852e78a">
<p local-id=3D"ed808f60-2386-4b76-8384-472999ddf1ea"><strong>Milestone Info=
rmation:</strong><br>
For each status milestone, display:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"a9f1055d-14af-48bc-9beb-1da5f647cd87">
<li local-id=3D"2f36c349-9db6-44ac-9d7e-5b841edd719f">
<p local-id=3D"9010ef39-8380-4c9f-978d-535ef6798173">Status name and descri=
ption</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3bd6564b-d21c-4c23-b7cc-3cb3b06c75c6">
<p local-id=3D"e1eb4553-9b95-4c03-be30-60729571797d">Date and time (dd/mm/y=
yyy hh:mm)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fb438f29-0cd8-4f9e-a156-756ef1c4b38c">
<p local-id=3D"7851341f-cb37-4d3d-99c6-6e306def0a45">User who performed act=
ion (name and role) or "System" for automatic actions</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"30202e97-c3df-4350-8372-4e1f4da2fa1c">
<p local-id=3D"b4521191-88df-4b58-a729-3004ea02d6c9">Action description (if=
 applicable, e.g., "Edit Request", "Registration Rejected")</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0399a72d-b18c-413b-bd20-9f558d966116">
<p local-id=3D"2b43a946-533f-47d8-8ee3-0477466e6f55">Reason (for rejections=
, cancellations, or approval requests)</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"8dc62ee4-dc5d-4522-b133-cf583d5a0216">
<p local-id=3D"7fd9ec9d-a980-4e12-8183-3c6d648da4fd"><strong>Timeline Layou=
t:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"bb9dcd19-3d7f-4455-88bd-cd5474c74a69">
<li local-id=3D"715ed15a-a819-4d1a-9e1a-6fce3ca3efcb">
<p local-id=3D"ba8c7019-9830-4edc-816c-1aa08097b750">Horizontal timeline fo=
r desktop view</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7adba126-d69a-40f0-9d18-1ef7c8667df3">
<p local-id=3D"3171a1ad-9de0-4a99-b61d-8c201095d1f3">Vertical timeline for =
mobile/tablet view</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9d44aa0f-fcce-4860-af96-4d38867e2ac5">
<p local-id=3D"e0b5f719-03ed-42c7-b516-9216d65f56e1">Responsive design that=
 adapts to screen size</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ba629b53-2c3d-42e2-999b-3e9721e24fb0">
<p local-id=3D"7068e7cc-003e-41e7-b9e9-8b62a1c457a0">Compact view by defaul=
t, expandable for details</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"78e1ba52-aeb8-421e-b8fe-2810f81a6d8b">
<p local-id=3D"52ca2b4a-bdc9-47ab-9754-4cafc798bfd7"><strong>Progress Indic=
ator:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"928fea2b-4793-421b-a75b-6665c9e81c08">
<li local-id=3D"d6b696a4-772f-4838-b903-2f92af488117">
<p local-id=3D"c0815a01-effc-471f-908f-fd75559f5dd0">Show current status pr=
ominently</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4cae2955-7aec-4b2f-a4fd-d8b12a5de77f">
<p local-id=3D"7a0769fd-c7e0-4293-b637-d1af45d08e40">Display progress perce=
ntage if applicable (e.g., course days completed)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"753c6fd0-e155-4617-839d-29a8a0430291">
<p local-id=3D"182537ca-4ceb-479e-9c4e-ec33905eba66">Show next expected mil=
estone or deadline</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"437bd66d-40c2-4d12-9b6b-7fa42794d528">
<p local-id=3D"b8da297f-02e1-4ce2-bd89-2af789a4bf47"><strong>Interactive Fe=
atures:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"7f1fd80e-ba35-4ef2-bf19-fa5f3296ae93">
<li local-id=3D"2012aee7-f6f9-4ea1-97d4-e29789e8082e">
<p local-id=3D"bfed7215-fedc-44c8-9ed5-1c9d2b7f5848">Hover over milestone: =
Tooltip with summary (status, date, user)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0f12e49a-892a-4056-aec6-af8bb0b5474e">
<p local-id=3D"e6fbfcdb-1690-427c-a3ce-10566e4e0739">Click milestone: Expan=
d to show full details</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8950f9c4-b449-4472-aa69-ab81781d898a">
<p local-id=3D"7f8f4a7e-d7e8-45a7-b837-6b78d9a4ec62">Toggle approval workfl=
ows: Show/hide WAITING_APPROVAL_EDIT and WAITING_APPROVAL_CANCEL milestones=
</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9d003659-01dd-43c7-80c1-e1eb4e042a00">
<p local-id=3D"9aa0b95f-8edf-4fcc-9368-e75662ab0a07">Export timeline: Optio=
n to export as PDF or image</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"c878cd9c-d31b-4109-bdeb-bbb9f3fea1ba"><strong>Data Requireme=
nts:</strong></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"0a=
521cf4-6132-4590-bcff-fd8367dc81e9" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr ac:local-id=3D"457d178f-86fa-483a-8654-694b0cddcd56">
<th data-local-id=3D"65c035fe-7d95-4e7d-892d-7a5b91324076" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"d0c23d08-ad94-41ac-92fe-1900967c736f">Field Name</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"5e4def29-48e7-49ce-a087-db5a20b4652d" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"23626bdd-0cb4-4817-be27-a59a325844d4">Data Type</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"f9722dbd-84d3-4063-a14d-985893d926f6" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"72d6e152-069c-4f12-b428-2f807af3910f">M/O/CM/D</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"bebf983f-170b-4229-8951-d6297a03ac9b" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"85c46067-d885-4718-8e06-3fd19dffa370">Description</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"d40e0e8f-3289-41de-9d92-30e465cf2a4d" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"e58d6836-0b2d-4241-b804-70bdc642ea15">Example</p></th>
</tr>
<tr ac:local-id=3D"539eb0d2-dbf9-468d-ad57-040464ecfd5f">
<td data-local-id=3D"bce18d11-39a6-4ef0-9e2c-7e7b3633f92a" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d8e7b726-49c7-48bb-b518-c1e736732f1d">Status</p></td>
