<p local-id=3D"4d017dee-6e30-47dc-b67f-314ca36abe6e"><strong>Business Rules=
:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"33b333e3-d6be-4c0f-a636-042962a6622a">
<li local-id=3D"3aa3cf37-3439-4370-bc5c-ead2d7460a9a">
<p local-id=3D"8fd2be35-04ea-435d-80f0-b9ac811656de"><strong>Timeline Displ=
ay Logic:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"ce8f56c7-b31c-4a84-893f-8ff6bb4ba856">
<li local-id=3D"2dc55a7f-3cb0-4452-8e93-b4d31d9c9cd7">
<p local-id=3D"33ac4414-0e88-42dd-9f47-92a5bef6b443">Only show statuses tha=
t have occurred (completed milestones)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"01c13e2e-87c1-4a62-901a-5288d5d0146d">
<p local-id=3D"bde0bbf6-2ac7-4321-aa51-06f776b6dfbb">Show current status wi=
th highlight and animation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"74fbdae8-e850-4937-89b0-d96d42d407f7">
<p local-id=3D"e38bef50-73af-4ed4-83b3-83e757800bac">Show next expected sta=
tus as pending (if applicable)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ebf18974-7c76-43df-97f1-4b6bb44081e8">
<p local-id=3D"291d1e8e-72f4-490c-9d97-f79076823c98">Approval workflows (WA=
ITING_APPROVAL_EDIT, WAITING_APPROVAL_CANCEL) shown only when relevant</p><=
/li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"2f731bf4-e0ea-43fd-9444-1de065e82a59">
<p local-id=3D"38ab16ff-329c-48fa-8699-2c3150f6acae"><strong>Status History=
 Tracking:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"d4061403-c4cb-4560-95bd-fcb837e1db27">
<li local-id=3D"ea393c6f-36bc-4a68-87e7-4dd567b88d56">
<p local-id=3D"8d630ba2-b244-49b9-8a85-0071c043e81c">System records all sta=
tus changes with timestamp and user</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f8ccb7ea-1d78-4a46-aa0d-4a2dd4ba54c8">
<p local-id=3D"8e6e082f-31d3-48d2-8f4c-999b54f6321c">Automatic actions (e.g=
., IN_PROGRESS on start date) marked as "System"</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1833d15d-9f12-4de0-9912-48bd824c4f37">
<p local-id=3D"df0aba6d-3552-4f72-a7f7-179688a93851">Approval workflows tra=
cked with request timestamp and approval/rejection timestamp</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ba5a451d-74a4-4ec7-8f36-e610d83db27e">
<p local-id=3D"93e335f6-1dd5-437b-a2fc-261f5f50763a">Rejection actions show=
 reason in timeline</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"d625b230-b2e7-4f86-ad7d-913bc8637802">
<p local-id=3D"225d846b-dd2d-4a8d-a6c3-27f9047edbbb"><strong>Auto-Cancellat=
ion Display:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"25a25e7a-6ace-44ea-b7f6-d88ee6bc2ffc">
<li local-id=3D"478e4cd3-58db-42ff-9f45-645c4502ff6b">
<p local-id=3D"e69e9183-bf40-4ffb-9f35-e490c46f689a">If course is auto-canc=
elled (not approved by start date), show CANCEL status</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fa71abd3-928a-49a0-8d7a-2c67f58d61d2">
<p local-id=3D"3beeee52-44de-4e62-a739-983409fe1969">Display cancellation r=
eason: "Not approved by course start date"</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d715a945-7e80-4c31-bd23-515cc0e54995">
<p local-id=3D"2c941685-b593-49c4-9a3a-65c7adc90c9a">Mark as automatic acti=
on by System</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"d4abea80-db04-4875-8eda-208f8c0d8395">
<p local-id=3D"0e959e70-2856-4703-a4d8-ae8371509370"><strong>Progress Calcu=
lation:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"5bc92c7a-870e-4df8-9ed1-f125c3122259">
<li local-id=3D"40912308-52d3-480d-a133-08c1189ab986">
<p local-id=3D"9372a416-69bb-47f6-abd8-62300a7cfa49">For IN_PROGRESS status=
: Calculate percentage based on course days completed</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b15ba4a5-17de-4cc4-9749-dc22f58be29d">
<p local-id=3D"d6105d24-d0bf-4f1b-b1f4-fbf750cfdf9c">Formula: (Days complet=
ed / Total course days) =C3=97 100%</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"dff65b9f-f997-4c86-b613-eda15ba38434">
<p local-id=3D"548d7faa-7b55-427c-a587-c8976b86e6df">Show current day numbe=
r (e.g., "Day 3 of 6")</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"29100b8c-dd1c-411b-9066-ccea971c9462">
<p local-id=3D"8f063fd8-7a2d-4c8c-9ac4-fc33153714b5"><strong>Timeline Sorti=
ng:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"12363be5-220b-428b-a4dd-3534b4997bed">
<li local-id=3D"f9c3f11b-6839-41a5-b236-250db830f463">
<p local-id=3D"edaf9ae0-bca5-4513-a303-bbc6e0691a2a">Sort by timestamp (chr=
onological order)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9c54a392-f2a9-40be-a14e-3d78fc884a21">
<p local-id=3D"771f52e5-9590-4e70-8f22-8f2cc064595c">Most recent status at =
right (horizontal) or bottom (vertical)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"03103cd9-7e72-47dc-be21-1e56777740be">
<p local-id=3D"d3ac2ffe-a522-47db-ad56-2a8a84c85263">Approval workflows ins=
erted chronologically</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"e40d8870-b376-4bdb-baed-e03d9ecddcf8"><strong>Authorization:=
</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"0068a180-59a3-4917-aeec-f3a5fd603c7c">
<li local-id=3D"e4302b5a-c155-4b6d-894c-6e93020b07bc">
<p local-id=3D"c6439ae7-7a35-4aa8-9ce1-4defbaee94d8"><strong>View Timeline:=
</strong> All users who can view course details</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"00065a80-97e9-4cd5-942b-123116b8cc5f">
<p local-id=3D"56acf3d8-07bc-41a8-b47d-4c554acf2e57"><strong>Export Timelin=
e:</strong> Admin, Master Role, Root Admin</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b8bd9b61-bc40-4bcd-9cf9-72a5d87d4c06">
<p local-id=3D"3b599038-7d55-4990-8ba9-693d1a3a3f43"><strong>Timeline data:=
</strong> Based on course viewing authorization rules</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"a45df5c5-2b30-4153-a7bc-118250933388">
<h3 local-id=3D"f97ef627-74d7-41c1-a531-cb546645b43c" id=3D"CourseDetailsSc=
reen-8.3.1.3CourseApprovalActions">8.3.1.3 Course Approval Actions</h3>
<p local-id=3D"d4f344f8-9b28-43ee-b6e8-da5d7cff2f1c"><strong>User Story:</s=
trong> <br>
AS a Head Channel, Lead Region, or authorized approver <br>
I NEED to approve or reject course-related actions from the Course Details =
screen <br>
SO THAT I can manage course registration, edits, and cancellations efficien=
tly</p>
<p local-id=3D"82e0e55e-d2b2-4df0-b225-4d5d928a2d6e"><strong>Overview:</str=
ong></p>
<p local-id=3D"d8d49bcc-086b-487e-b4b9-8938f4525c32">The Course Details scr=
een provides access to approval actions for:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"3a6c020c-b936-4bbb-9b94-47b704634fa1">
<li local-id=3D"128c2d88-e683-4321-b801-0fc93c791096">
<p local-id=3D"8479d5ff-8221-4da7-b72b-edf1e86f9994">Course Registration (S=
ection 8.4.2)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8cdf8309-b4f9-4d35-a0bd-70882a39839a">
<p local-id=3D"6ac849ce-eb96-4a68-bdb9-f41b8a879611">Course Edit Requests (=
Section 8.5.2)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0e2e8be6-fb48-475d-ac45-fcd71ab2e490">
<p local-id=3D"ee8e6f85-01a0-48ef-a0be-14935a4602b2">Course Cancellation Re=
quests (Section 8.6.2)</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"1e9bb51d-75d7-403d-b3a4-c5532933dcea"><strong>Approval Autho=
rization Matrix:</strong></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
