<p local-id=3D"02a120e5-c92e-482a-a40d-718f72ae72f6"><strong>History Entry =
Format:</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"3c14c2ea-7c24-4d1f-8264-af7770b6d3b5">All entries include:</=
p>
<ul local-id=3D"762c9f2f-3804-426f-86d0-1aff5183c334">
<li local-id=3D"4ae66322-ece0-4069-a5eb-b633f7408ee9">
<p local-id=3D"ad463243-d623-4aa9-85ab-df65878de41a"><strong>User ID:</stro=
ng> User who performed the action</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"66b5323a-fa0c-4872-9721-6875353783cf">
<p local-id=3D"cb4124a4-e2f7-4040-8435-f581b7c94a72"><strong>Timestamp:</st=
rong> Date and time (dd/mm/yyyy hh:mm)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"445e5639-dfc4-4d4a-add1-0a60bc4b628c">
<p local-id=3D"dcdd212b-b130-4dfb-8dc9-660cfaefbbb7"><strong>Action Type:</=
strong> Type of modification or action</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"30006a20-320a-44ec-a5fa-e4d0475fcac9">
<p local-id=3D"1ebb5ac6-36ff-4035-bd79-0562aa90f682"><strong>Field Changed:=
</strong> Field name (for updates)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d621ceb3-a601-42ee-ad90-b1930e8fc59d">
<p local-id=3D"04f33ba0-e0d3-4dc6-8698-e5aa060f4ce2"><strong>Old Value:</st=
rong> Previous value (for updates)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f709fd6b-b3e2-4d71-a71a-f9c16b53e9a6">
<p local-id=3D"41bfbbc8-16ff-41f9-a868-64daf8ddb4df"><strong>New Value:</st=
rong> New value (for updates)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"aea5a7b9-c74a-4717-aa4d-709fe4a3ae2c">
<p local-id=3D"3f08f990-635b-4fb9-9688-b793d05f129c"><strong>Reason:</stron=
g> Reason for action (for rejections, cancellations, edits)</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"119bdc2d-4d04-4113-99f3-310217e72844"><strong>Business Rules=
:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"c57167a9-8951-40ca-ad62-92c4a8c7dbb9">
<li local-id=3D"6e8ea01d-33cf-4063-ad5a-e380a1235874">
<p local-id=3D"931c9933-e71a-488a-a371-dbb4840a569a"><strong>History Record=
ing:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"e52459b9-b4e7-4152-8ab7-0077856a8ea3">
<li local-id=3D"53111aca-2673-4cf9-87a9-5a67438240bb">
<p local-id=3D"9107a887-4e38-475b-ade9-577d14d44add">All course modificatio=
ns are automatically recorded</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cd8e5eec-ffab-453a-a696-d4227b367499">
<p local-id=3D"bbe41e67-f8fd-4de0-8aff-624d5c82f6ba">System actions are mar=
ked with "System" as user</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ce04855f-319b-4eb8-affa-c10a62d27844">
<p local-id=3D"51a75f20-9252-4dea-952b-ede1824108ee">Manual actions record =
the user who performed them</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"0375d665-ecca-43ed-a2e3-c5331d01101e">
<p local-id=3D"2c055dbe-ea17-489e-9fbf-bf18dbdadf28"><strong>History Displa=
y:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"1197524f-9da3-4994-b0c3-202de177f3b9">
<li local-id=3D"73d84ab3-379d-4b9f-a92f-3ab2db234f06">
<p local-id=3D"7ddc87d7-5a0b-408e-a21f-69f1b24acd84">History entries displa=
yed in chronological order (newest first)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3bd8c80f-dd92-4689-ae65-c5d91ca76c47">
<p local-id=3D"b727f3dc-3b7e-409d-88f0-08249ad8b45a">History entries are re=
ad-only</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"766aaa9f-e4a0-4aeb-a061-e5ae95a82733">
<p local-id=3D"4a140dda-26d6-4c76-92e4-8c61e643d24b">History cannot be dele=
ted or modified</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"06c17da9-6dec-4721-8608-bbd04eafcc14">
<p local-id=3D"0a464fc4-68eb-4d13-97a6-fc8713cfec54"><strong>History Access=
:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"8be9079f-bd14-47f4-a7eb-5afc540e3e2c">
<li local-id=3D"707233f3-5709-47fc-9973-705b9bec9446">
<p local-id=3D"14550a40-c1fa-40a0-86ed-e093137777c3">All users who can view=
 course details can view history</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8ff909b1-62b2-40d8-ae83-a8d0d4b4fe1e">
<p local-id=3D"89894e09-d131-4251-b5df-91cc3e47b67b">History is displayed i=
n Course Details =E2=86=92 History tab</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ol>
<hr local-id=3D"a6cbd8cd-04e0-4d07-9939-61fba188c946">
