<p local-id=3D"eaad8d44-758e-48e1-8c81-9d941d130655"><strong>Course Time in=
 Non-Continuous Days:</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"26f27f22-f98f-4a76-92ac-34d32e6d6d8c"><strong>User Story:</s=
trong> <br>
AS AN admin/trainer/head/lead <br>
I CAN manage the non-continuous course <br>
SO THAT the course time can be tracked correctly</p>
<p local-id=3D"f203045c-dd57-4403-906a-503c90a0e0b8"><strong>Acceptance Cri=
teria:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"c3629420-79a6-4269-9e6a-dddf3e350f58">
<li local-id=3D"9807aefd-845f-4c1e-9f11-4db0e82286e0">
<p local-id=3D"84c0f2e4-91f6-46b7-976f-27251cf4209c">Authorized users can e=
dit planning (time of stages)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6e6034aa-0a8f-4d82-ad1f-f35497e984a2">
<p local-id=3D"617e3be7-a49d-48f8-b09c-8f9c8143450b">Course can skip days (=
holidays, scheduled one stage per week, etc.)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"65660405-7739-4886-b09f-84a80386b939">
<p local-id=3D"7dc621e5-17fe-4c76-8c8f-90375f28d235">End date updated autom=
atically according to planning changes</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"794a6bc9-66fc-40e2-ac52-ac97b397bc5c">
<p local-id=3D"0913d34b-8fba-489e-9f13-5f0adaa4f482">PIC/Master Calendar au=
tomatically updated to show skip days</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"0e36b96c-aac3-49b1-96c8-14e720b73b78"><strong>Example:</stro=
ng></p>
<ul local-id=3D"876cdec0-b1db-44cf-97d2-835a228f9a35">
<li local-id=3D"f74a6b93-4b7b-4bd1-9347-e1efb76cc0d3">
<p local-id=3D"f699df5c-4818-4941-a626-49b89acaace9">Course X has 4 stages,=
 skip date T</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f432084b-1929-41b9-9a46-87fe8487761c">
<p local-id=3D"147ecc1b-85bf-4e30-99d7-7ea041f6a015">Start Date: T-1</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"90668a3a-58f1-4c6a-8ed6-583ff4dc1516">
<p local-id=3D"9e7309ff-5629-44e7-8c31-bc86e9778a00">Skip: T</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fbe24af4-d10b-4f90-8d1a-62f64ba8aa2f">
<p local-id=3D"144e75d7-c10c-4195-bc7d-e507ad519717">End Date: T+1</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"72afe555-41ea-4f98-b6f7-503c3a9dd298">Planning:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"744f0874-b451-4cf2-85b2-0a1f6a8ffa82">
<li local-id=3D"61d4a697-cee6-4f44-9322-08d461016695">
<p local-id=3D"0761a490-c914-4d00-8cce-bd854625225a">Stage 1: T-1 AM</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"9fa73ff0-7815-41ae-8b30-cdcf282358e3">
<p local-id=3D"9ac95ef7-cf61-4061-bf15-5d82b84da5da">Stage 2: T-1 PM</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"6f1e1d65-1db7-46fb-9eb2-dd3252007b1f">
<p local-id=3D"346b3de2-0ee8-4ea9-8dc3-e275b9cb866d">Stage 3: T+1 AM</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"ba9ae758-fc34-407c-9c88-05489c059767">
<p local-id=3D"c10d1fbc-145c-44b5-8eac-d5c3199a367d">Stage 4: T+1 PM</p></l=
i>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"ab3f0b18-537f-4824-bb6f-ba2b6cf52eb4"><strong>Business Rules=
:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"bcfc3230-c945-44f4-9707-99349bb34eff">
<li local-id=3D"8ee82361-6bfd-47e2-9d17-0b40561af09e">
<p local-id=3D"96b6d292-e292-4657-b9b7-09ab5e0172f7"><strong>Planning Edit =
Authorization:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"8b6c4aed-1f21-4738-b68d-41c401639436">
<li local-id=3D"e076cb88-90cd-4d09-a0ce-b059cf91a45f">
<p local-id=3D"5c0fbeb9-4700-4a42-bc43-3021075846d9">Admin, Trainer, Head C=
hannel, Lead Region can edit planning</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5dd8b99f-2b4b-4c72-8373-042d46aea7f8">
<p local-id=3D"f7e3b03f-7e77-47dd-bbe2-875c22a60e87">Planning can be edited=
 when course status is NEW, REGISTERED, or APPROVED</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ae608f02-143b-49e9-81e8-f3150fbb97f6">
<p local-id=3D"81891917-529f-42f2-b747-f39ca460f253">Planning cannot be edi=
ted when course is IN_PROGRESS or FINISHED</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"855093fa-f862-43a0-943e-3a428d96d656">
<p local-id=3D"6db5cc00-d6ff-4a70-8933-613003db0737"><strong>Stage Manageme=
nt:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"a4ac38ff-7286-49a0-8311-e46bc6f449d4">
<li local-id=3D"974a13af-a2ef-482b-a0aa-24627bbd972f">
<p local-id=3D"681948ff-a681-4c3a-8152-78f5b1b37b3d">Stages can be added, e=
dited, or deleted</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"09cf155f-e860-4009-8c20-712002ac3e84">
<p local-id=3D"257f07dc-c408-4094-be7e-62e742b2f0df">Each stage has date, t=
ime (AM/PM), and trainer assignment</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8d2139cf-fca4-43ba-9236-62e9e5ec074b">
<p local-id=3D"7f29dd62-14a0-48a8-bac3-7d327f7421c3">Co-trainer can be assi=
gned per stage</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"5b7471b5-2e36-4ee5-bc6d-6e205d99f82b">
<p local-id=3D"9a8d8070-58de-4b25-8d9b-efcd2c99a23d"><strong>Date Calculati=
on:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"3a090cae-844d-48a7-8706-70f291b048ad">
<li local-id=3D"d6c402d3-2bd0-413b-83b3-0d9210f08b41">
<p local-id=3D"996e247a-f5a0-43e5-b7d6-295d00f701b6">End date automatically=
 calculated from last stage date</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6e982752-f7c5-4a1a-8ba4-0f07c2ff1471">
<p local-id=3D"93165b9f-7a11-4d06-b952-a431a98a6a6d">Skip days are excluded=
 from course duration calculation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"75e8617f-7f73-4cb1-87d7-106a9487db7a">
<p local-id=3D"ebd853d0-5a42-47c8-895c-8514967d1f79">Calendar views reflect=
 skip days</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ol>
<hr local-id=3D"bd68b5a2-7262-4bfb-8186-2dcaf54a28c2">
